    <para><!--Warning: text element with unused attributes: color="#000000" fontsize="90%" -->All
    you need to do is plug the agenda items from this chapter into the teal
    area where it says “Agenda items.” The agenda items are:<itemizedlist>
        <listitem>
          <para><!--Warning: text element with unused attributes: color="#000000" fontsize="90%" -->Selection:
          facilitator, leader &amp; secretary</para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para><!--Warning: text element with unused attributes: color="#000000" fontsize="90%" -->Infrastructure
          and communication</para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para><!--Warning: text element with unused attributes: color="#000000" fontsize="90%" -->Gather
          items for the backlog</para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para><!--Warning: text element with unused attributes: color="#000000" fontsize="90%" -->Prioritize
          the backlog</para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para><!--Warning: text element with unused attributes: color="#000000" fontsize="90%" -->Add
          new members? (y/n)</para>
        </listitem>

