      <section xml:id="consentroles">
        <title>Define the role and the term</title>

        <para><!--Warning: text element with unused attributes: color="#000000" fontsize="90%" -->Before
        you can select anyone into any roles, people need to understand what
        the roles entail and how long a person will serve. By default, we
        suggest you use six months as a term.</para>

        <para><!--Warning: text element with unused attributes: color="#000000" fontsize="90%" -->The
        role descriptions on page <xref linkend="roledescriptions"/><!--Warning: text element with unused attributes: color="#000000" fontsize="90%" -->
