      </section>

      <section xml:id="qualifications">
        <title><!--Warning: text element with unused attributes: color="#808080" -->Gather
        qualifications and get consent</title>

        <para><!--Warning: text element with unused attributes: color="#000000" fontsize="90%" -->Next,
        for each of the roles, compile a list of qualifications and qualities
        that a person filling that role should have, similar to the table on
        page <xref linkend="qualifications"/><!--Warning: text element with unused attributes: color="#000000" fontsize="90%" -->.
        In rounds, let each person say one item until you run out of ideas.
        When the list seems ready, ask for consent. “Is this list good enough
        to base our decision on and to go on to the next step?”. You can check
        for consent by using handsigns like thumbs up.</para>

        <informaltable>
          <!--Warning: passing through `tabular` element: -->

          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td><!--Warning: passing through `p` element: --><!--Warning: text element with unused attributes: color="#000000" fontsize="90%" -->darkerteal
              <emphasis role="bold">Role</emphasis></td>

              <td><!--Warning: passing through `p` element: --><emphasis
              role="bold">Qualities and qualifications</emphasis></td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td><!--Warning: passing through `p` element: --><!--Warning: text element with unused attributes: color="#000000" fontsize="90%" -->Leader</td>

              <td><!--Warning: passing through `p` element: --><!--Warning: text element with unused attributes: color="#000000" fontsize="90%" -->  <!--Warning: text element with unused attributes: color="#000000" fontsize="90%" width="0.0pt" -->•<!--Warning: text element with unused attributes: color="#000000" fontsize="90%" -->  Good
              at tracking tasks <!--Warning: passing through `p` element: --><!--Warning: text element with unused attributes: color="#000000" fontsize="90%" -->•
              <!--Warning: passing through `p` element: --><!--Warning: text element with unused attributes: color="#000000" fontsize="90%" -->Good
              follow-up <!--Warning: passing through `p` element: --><!--Warning: text element with unused attributes: color="#000000" fontsize="90%" -->•
              <!--Warning: passing through `p` element: --><!--Warning: text element with unused attributes: color="#000000" fontsize="90%" -->Communication
              skills <!--Warning: passing through `p` element: --><!--Warning: text element with unused attributes: color="#000000" fontsize="90%" -->•
              <!--Warning: passing through `p` element: --><!--Warning: text element with unused attributes: color="#000000" fontsize="90%" -->Trusted
              by the group</td>
            </tr>

