              <!--Warning: passing through `p` element: --><!--Warning: text element with unused attributes: color="#000000" fontsize="90%" -->Facilitator</td>

              <td><!--Warning: passing through `p` element: --><!--Warning: text element with unused attributes: color="#000000" fontsize="90%" -->  <!--Warning: text element with unused attributes: color="#000000" fontsize="90%" width="0.0pt" -->•<!--Warning: text element with unused attributes: color="#000000" fontsize="90%" -->  Experience/willingness
              to learn <!--Warning: passing through `p` element: --><!--Warning: text element with unused attributes: color="#000000" fontsize="90%" -->•
              <!--Warning: passing through `p` element: --><!--Warning: text element with unused attributes: color="#000000" fontsize="90%" -->Gentle
              but focused <!--Warning: passing through `p` element: --><!--Warning: text element with unused attributes: color="#000000" fontsize="90%" -->•
              <!--Warning: passing through `p` element: --><!--Warning: text element with unused attributes: color="#000000" fontsize="90%" -->Multi-partial
              (hold own opinion lightly)</td>
            </tr>

