              at multitasking <!--Warning: passing through `p` element: --><!--Warning: text element with unused attributes: color="#000000" fontsize="90%" -->•
              <!--Warning: passing through `p` element: --><!--Warning: text element with unused attributes: color="#000000" fontsize="90%" -->Fast
              typing <!--Warning: passing through `p` element: --><!--Warning: text element with unused attributes: color="#000000" fontsize="90%" -->•
              <!--Warning: passing through `p` element: --><!--Warning: text element with unused attributes: color="#000000" fontsize="90%" -->IT
              skills</td>
